#: ../../../source/index.rst:9
msgid "Welcome to Emscripten SDK |release|"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/index.rst:11
msgid ""
"This documentation contains everything you need to :ref:`start developing "
"<Tutorial>` with the Emscripten SDK."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/index.rst:13
msgid "Emscripten logo"
msgstr "Emscripten 標誌"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:19
msgid ""
"Emscripten is a complete compiler toolchain to WebAssembly, using LLVM, with "
"a special focus on speed, size, and the Web platform."
msgstr ""
"Emscripten 是一套完整的編譯器工具鏈，能將程式編譯為 WebAssembly，使用 LLVM，"
"特別強調速度、大小以及 Web 平台。"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:23
msgid ""
":doc:`Docs <docs/index>` `GitHub <https://github.com/emscripten-core/"
"emscripten>`_"
msgstr ""
":doc:`文件 <docs/index>` `GitHub <https://github.com/emscripten-core/"
"emscripten>`_"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:29
msgid "Porting"
msgstr "移植"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:31
msgid ""
"Compile your existing projects written in C or C++ -- or any language that "
"uses `LLVM <https://llvm.org/>`_ -- to browsers, `Node.js <https://nodejs."
"org/>`_, or `wasm runtimes <https://v8.dev/blog/emscripten-standalone-"
"wasm#running-in-wasm-runtimes>`_."
msgstr ""
"將您現有以 C 或 C++ 撰寫的專案（或任何使用 `LLVM <https://llvm.org/>`_ 的語"
"言）編譯到瀏覽器、`Node.js <https://nodejs.org/>`_ 或 `wasm 執行環境 "
"<https://v8.dev/blog/emscripten-standalone-wasm#running-in-wasm-runtimes>`_。"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:33
msgid "APIs"
msgstr "API"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:35
msgid ""
"Emscripten converts OpenGL into WebGL, and has support for familiar APIs "
"like SDL, pthreads, and POSIX, as well as Web APIs and JavaScript."
msgstr ""
"Emscripten 將 OpenGL 轉換為 WebGL，並支援像 SDL、pthreads 和 POSIX 等常見 "
"API，以及 Web API 和 JavaScript。"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:37
msgid "Fast"
msgstr "快速"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:39
msgid ""
"Thanks to the combination of LLVM, Emscripten, `Binaryen <https://github.com/"
"WebAssembly/binaryen>`_, and `WebAssembly <https://webassembly.org/>`_, the "
"output is compact and runs at near-native speed."
msgstr ""
"得益於 LLVM、Emscripten、`Binaryen <https://github.com/WebAssembly/"
"binaryen>`_ 與 `WebAssembly <https://webassembly.org/>`_ 的組合，輸出結果體積"
"精簡且執行速度接近原生。"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:41
msgid "Interested to learn more?"
msgstr "想進一步了解嗎？"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:43
msgid ""
"Read our :doc:`About page <docs/introducing_emscripten/about_emscripten>`!"
msgstr ""
"閱讀我們的\\ :doc:`關於頁面 <docs/introducing_emscripten/"
"about_emscripten>`\\ ！"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:45
msgid "Ready to get started?"
msgstr "準備好開始了嗎？"

#: ../../../source/index.rst:47
msgid ""
